      • findDefaultKey

        public static String findDefaultKey(String key,
                    Class clazz,
                    Map<String,String> settings)
        looks for a default value for a key based on the simpleName of a class suffixed by .key. This method will traverse all Parameterizable superclasses in search of a default.
        Parameters:
        key -
        Returns:
        the key to the default for a Parameterizable class

      • setup

        Parameters:

        args - the arguments with keys and values
        settings -
